John stand before them, they began to question them: “By what power or in what name have you done this?”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:4:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then Peter was filled with the Holy Spirit and said to them, “Rulers of the people and elders: "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add of Israel"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 23:13","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:5","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 23:13","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":13},{"label":"Ac 4:5","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add of Israel"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:4:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If we are being examined today about a good deed done to a disabled man, by what means he was healed, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:4:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"let it be known to all of you and to all the people of Israel, that by the name of Jesus Christ of Nazareth, whom you crucified and whom God raised from the dead —by him this man is standing here before you healthy. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:24","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:6","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 2:24","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":24},{"label":"Ac 3:6","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:4:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This Jesus is"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:4:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"There is salvation in no one else, for there is no other name under heaven given to people by which we must be saved.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 1:21","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":21,"le